# ╭⋟─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╮
#   Sensible defaults to ignore in any repository. Indvidual repositoriies
#   can add additional things to this list, but this should cover all the
#   basic scenarios you run into.
# ╰─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────⋞╯

# Files and folders that the OS uses for various purposes.
*._*
*.orig
*.swp
*~
.DS_Store
.DS_Store?
.svn
.Trash-*
main.tfvars
Thumbs.db

# Random files we probably never want to see.
dump.rdb
*.phar
*.cache

# Things we want to exclude for safety's sake.
.env

# Folders created by the IDE for various purposes, generally completely
# useless to include in a repository.
*.idea
.idea
.vscode

# PHP and NodeJS package installation folders.
node_modules
vendor
